29/12/2022
        -       Virtual environment
                        
                        Create a virtual environment: 
                        python3 -m venv <name of virtual environment>

                        Activate virtual environment:
                        . venv/bin/activate

                        Deactivate virtual environmt:
                        deactivate

                        Create a requirements text file:
                        pip freeze > requirements.txt

                        




